  "analyst_note": "CVE-2021-35211: Pre-authentication RCE in SolarWinds Serv-U FTP Server and MFT Server, exploited in the wild by APT (DEV-0322 / UNC2630). The exploit targets the SSH component \u2014 Serv-U exposes SSH on port 22 (default) and the banner 'SSH-2.0-Serv-U_X.Y.Z' is visible. Nmap -sV will typically extract the version from the SSH banner. Fixed in Serv-U 15.2.3 Hotfix 2 (15.2.3.2). If the Serv-U SSH service is internet-exposed, treat as critical priority.",
